00:20:47.170 --> 00:20:54.840
So we offer what's called DFP,
Double Click for Publishers,

00:20:54.840 --> 00:20:57.340
Double Click Ad Exchange.

00:20:57.340 --> 00:20:58.740
We also offer AdMob.

00:20:58.740 --> 00:21:03.090
So AdMob is the fact of putting
advertising on a

00:21:03.090 --> 00:21:05.460
mobile application.

00:21:05.460 --> 00:21:10.890
And for sales you can use Google
Play and Google Wallet.

00:21:10.890 --> 00:21:12.970
And we also offer
carrier billing

00:21:12.970 --> 00:21:14.220
for some other purpose.

00:21:16.650 --> 00:21:22.810
So, yes, in app display
is probably what we're

00:21:22.810 --> 00:21:24.810
interested in today.

00:21:24.810 --> 00:21:27.540
The idea is that you
put advertising

00:21:27.540 --> 00:21:30.600
in the app, of course.

00:21:30.600 --> 00:21:34.850
So the idea is that the idea of
advertising is embedded in

00:21:34.850 --> 00:21:37.540
the mobile application.

00:21:37.540 --> 00:21:43.880
And then the business model is
based around the fact that the

00:21:43.880 --> 00:21:47.290
