on a cost per click.

00:21:47.290 --> 00:21:53.790
So the ad is displayed on the
application, and when a user

00:21:53.790 --> 00:21:56.590
clicks on the ad, then you
will receive money.

00:21:56.590 --> 00:22:00.330
